EXPENSE TRACKER(django)

A simple and user-friendly EXPENSE TRACKER WEB App built using (Django).  
It allows users to add, view, and analyze expenses with a clean dashboard and a category-wise pie chart.

features
    User authentication(login/Logout)
    Add & manage daily expenses
    View all expense with category, date and amount
    Total expense summary
    Clean UI

Tech Stack
    Django(backend)
    HTML, CSS(frontend)
    SQLite(database)
    Matplotlib(chart)
    Git, Github


